</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/3YUe8BMYMP8" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/11/08/lenovo-unwire-special-offer-2021-11/notebook/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=lenovo-unwire-special-offer-2021-11</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>黃明志新歌 NFT 販賣    12 小時勁賺 660 萬港元</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/RTAWAM9qiIo/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 08 Nov 2021 09:24:00 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[NFT]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1070250</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>雖然《玻璃心》被多方封殺，不過馬來西亞歌手黃明志通過網路 NFT「非同質化代幣」架構發售新歌，在 12 小時就 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>雖然《玻璃心》被多方封殺，不過馬來西亞歌手黃明志通過網路 NFT「非同質化代幣」架構發售新歌，在 12 小時就賺了約 85 萬美元（約港幣 660 萬元），令到 NFT 成為網路上的熱門話題。</p><p>所謂 NFT「非同質化代幣」，就是區塊鏈上的數據單位，歌手可以上載其歌曲成為 「非同質化代幣」，並建立副本。聽眾可以加密貨幣購買這些「非同質化代幣」，而歌手就能賺取收入，但仍然保留對歌曲的版權，且能去掉中間平台（如 Spotify）的抽佣。馬來西亞歌手黃明志近日就表明「用 NFT 對抗世界」，他即席為此題材作了一首歌，並拍攝了 20 張相片，上傳到 NFT 平台售賣。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-08-15.50.26.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070252" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-08-15.50.26-694x403.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="403" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-08-15.50.26-694x403.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-08-15.50.26-768x447.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-08-15.50.26.jpg 774w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-08-15.50.42.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070253" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-08-15.50.42-694x400.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="400" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-08-15.50.42-694x400.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-08-15.50.42-768x443.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-08-15.50.42.jpg 777w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>而上載了僅僅 3 小時，黃明志的歌曲就已經賣完，總共賺取了等值 85 萬美元的虛擬貨幣。黃明志的作品《玻璃心 Fragile》還有《飆高音》都有放上 NFT 售賣。黃明志表示，感謝大家用行動支持藝術創作者，他自己不會將這筆虛擬貨幣兌現，希望能永遠在虛擬世界裡流通，以對抗世界銀行。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-08-15.50.51.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070254" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-08-15.50.51-694x402.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="402" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-08-15.50.51-694x402.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-08-15.50.51-768x445.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-08-15.50.51.jpg 774w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_24983"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/oa-bo2AUrCw?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p></p><div class="feedflare">
